name: NFTZoo #04 Kandula
description: Please help and free some of the most stunning creatures from NFTZoo captivity!  All animals in the zoo are graffiti inspired, hand crafted, one off, rare specimens. Each one unique and beautiful in their own way.  We are delighted to welcome #04 Kandula, an elephant conceived by artificial insemination, with legendary status, who unified a nation nearly 2,000 years ago.
